<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>KANNIH VAWLEI SERTU CH54</title>
<key>Eb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Kannih vawlei sertu, Kan Pa Pathian a si, Hi hngalhnak ca kan hna a
 ngam, Thinphannak a um lo, Kan nih vawlei sertu, Kan Pa Pathian a si, Van
 le vawlei, Fing, tlang, rili, Lianhngannak in a ser.

[V2]
 Kannih vawlei sertu, Kan Pa Pathian a si, Amah lianhnak le
 khuaruahhar, Kannih sin a langhter, Pathian vawlei cungah, Dawhnak tampi
 a um, Va phun dangdang, Pangpar tam zong, Pathian lawmhnak a si.

[V3]
 Kannih vawlei sertu, Kan Pa Pathian a si, Thatlonak cu Thawng
 hmanhsehlaw, Uktu Pathian a si, Raldoh a dih rih lo, Jesuh nih a tei lai,
 Amah thawngin, vawlei le van remnak kha a si lai.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>54</hymn_number>
</song>